{"tid":25499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家陣係咪無人識講「籌期」？","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T13:08:26.000Z","uid":3656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b941a9655c55f746a76b69507b5fa1a0b32b784","tid":25499,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"個個淨係識講「眾籌」呢啲蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd374cc102c9d6df5787847376b3fb78ceadebd8","tid":25499,"uid":46021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"旗"},{"pid":"1ad8a31edb962f8d8fe63809ee40bb45aee0f921","tid":25499,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"籌旗 其實 借錢 只係型d<br />\n你果兩隻字 其實 kick start咁  做乜要講蝗語"},{"pid":"7f6a0a3b7d06d9fcfdc53ce2084b4b86ae46283e","tid":25499,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>籌旗 其實 借錢 只係型d<br />\n你果兩隻字 其實 kick start咁  做乜要講蝗語</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n群眾募資（英語：Crowd-funding），又稱群眾集資、公眾集資或群募；<span style=\"color: red;\">中國地區多簡稱眾籌</span>、群眾籌資。"},{"pid":"3bd3eb7137474e397db16a0c9b144d9a727fc256","tid":25499,"uid":57714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"923bcca152afb806ece436c52c111635426325ab","tid":25499,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>籌旗 其實 借錢 只係型d<br />\n你果兩隻字 其實 kick start咁  做乜要講蝗語</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n群眾募資（英語：Crowd-funding），又稱群眾集資、公眾集資或群募；<span style=\"color: red;\">中國地區多簡稱眾籌</span>、群眾籌資。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n「籌期」意思係籌錢，通常係遇上突發緊急需要，或者屎淋尿瀨嘅情形，先去到要「籌期」。<br />\n<br />\n同普通跑山借錢唔同嘅係，「籌期」所做嘅嘢，好多時係為大眾福利，或出於義氣。有啲人叫呢種募捐行為「搭棚」，其實意思係一樣。都係集資解決燃眉之急，「籌期」過關。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解錢又叫做期呢？點解旗又唔得呢？據筆者所知，「籌期」係應該嚟自監房術語。因為監房嘅工作係以時期做單位，做完一期工種就會調去做另一期工種，例如車衣工作叫「車衣期」、廚房工作叫「廚房期」等，每期有每期糧。如果囚友有需要夾份買嘢，或有人需要其他囚友幫手，就會吹雞集合大家嘅糧期去做嘢，呢啲就係所謂「籌期」。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，大家食飯AA制又叫「籌期」，同事夾份買六合彩又叫「籌期」，實在有啲濫。「籌期」係一個神聖嘅呼籲。「籌」到嘅「期」係要用得其所，否則大家辛勤工作所得，無私捐畀你原來係用嚟搞埋啲無謂嘢，咁我下期真係唔會再籌畀你！<br />\n<br />\nKickstarter 正正可以用籌期表達"},{"pid":"e47586594b6c0ac9256753308c99cb3e224effc7","tid":25499,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"唔係籌旗咩？"},{"pid":"3bc798cc0161c8238c66f4cd28a64d544b2e3fe2","tid":25499,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"你肯比我，我咪同你講囉"},{"pid":"26dd5cde724d39130758c79949766af6b61f95a0","tid":25499,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0531d9f2c575cbce8c796ecc6a3fe22c6efe77ea","tid":25499,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efd96c970b3aaefdb683e7ae8c4c55754a80fcd6","tid":25499,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係籌旗咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面解釋咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcdd569f8e9e0c4f06caa06f9cdf620003bc56d","tid":25499,"uid":39295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"點解又唔講「夾錢」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23675d56aa108f027983e0196ebdbc18a4353f90","tid":25499,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"旗呀"},{"pid":"9c33c6a8cfdfcce66ac080da73176e4883fad07c","tid":25499,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"雜支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9f4171a7fc912955f9cccfe03d22c8efaf0ab0","tid":25499,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"籌旗 / 跑山  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/